= Typographic Symbols

Typographic symbol rules automatically convert text to proper typographic symbols.

== Em Dash

This sentence uses an em dash -- like this.

Word--word creates an em dash.

== Ellipsis

This sentence uses an ellipsis... like this.

== Arrows

This shows a right arrow ->

This shows a double right arrow =>

This shows a left arrow <-

This shows a double left arrow <=

== Apostrophes

It's a contraction.

Don't do that.

